            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_416gc' title='Col. 416GC &mdash; HL Deb 05 February 2004 vol 656 c416GC' name='column_416gc' href='#column_416gc' rel='bookmark'>416GC</a>
            through major or minor re-organisation, and we are not quite sure how they will then be described. "Area", is a neutral term and can cover a multiplicity of things.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-05019'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040205_GCR_31'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-susan-thomas' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040205_GCR_31' title='Link to this speech by Ms Susan Thomas' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
