      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-05144'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040205_GCR_156' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 95 and 96 not moved</span>.]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-05145'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040205_GCR_157' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Anelay of St Johns</span> moved Amendment No. 97:
        <q>Page 13, line 2, leave out from "and" to end of line 4 and insert "the Lord Chancellor</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-05146'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040205_GCR_158' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
