        <q>Page 13, line 15, leave out from "and" to "before" in line 17 and insert "the Lord Chancellor</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-05157'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040205_GCR_169' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
